snippet.title: Rotoscape - Teaser Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's another gameplay video showing what Rotoscape is like.

Rotoscape is an minimalistic action puzzle game where you rotate oncoming shapes in order to survive your decent into the Shapiverse, with a bouncing soundtrack by Geoplex!

Coming soon to a device near you (Steam to start with)! Join our discord for more information.

Created by Last Abyss Inc.
---
More information over at our discord: https://discord.gg/MAtA3g8
